item.title: CVE-2022-32512|2024-08-03T07:46:43.362Z -- schneider%20electric -- canbrass
item.description: A CWE-119: Improper Restriction of Operations within the Bounds of a Memory Buffer vulnerability exists that could cause remote code execution when a command which exploits this vulnerability is utilized. Affected Products: CanBRASS (Versions prior to V7.5.1)
